name: Proper Heroine
description:
Whether in real life or in fiction A woman who is admired and admired is destined to have both a beautiful appearance and a well-rounded personality.

But does it really exist, a woman who is both innocent, innocent, and optimistic? At the same time, she is smart and gets along well with the people around her? Not only that She has never wronged anyone? To be loved by the man they always wanted?

Can a smart person who gets along with everyone really stay innocent?
Will there really be people in this world who have never misunderstood others?
A woman who has been loved and wooed by many men and she has never rejected anyone even knowing. Can you really maintain a pure heart?

Isn't this kind of story too funny?
Or perhaps behind this beautiful façade is full of thorns.
